column4: Tesla begins sales of cheaper Model 3 car variant in China
column5: BEIJING/SHANGHAI U.S. electric vehicle maker Tesla Inc said it will start taking orders in China on Friday for a lower-priced version of its Model 3 car  as it seeks to accelerate China sales hit by trade friction between Washington and Beijing. | Video

column4: UPDATE 3-Tesla begins sales of cheaper Model 3 car variant in China
column5: * Tesla says sales of 433 000 yuan variant to begin on Friday

column4: Tesla starts selling cheaper Model 3 car in China
column5: SHANGHAI  Feb 1 U.S. electric carmaker Tesla Inc said it will start taking orders in China on Friday for a lower-priced version of its Model 3 vehicle  whose price will start at 433 000 yuan  ($64 300.56).
